 only available to customers on the latest release of sage c accounting and requires a computer with internet explorer  firefox or chrome and a highspeed internet connection sage  data may be accessed from more than one device at a time by one individual each however only one has full access while the others have read only access and there are limits as to the amount of data that can be accessed data access is subject to internet provider network availability and occasional downtime due to system and server maintenance × get a personalized demo of sage  your browser does not support iframes close × sage  accounting customer testimonial close × sage  accounting customer testimonial close × sage  accounting customer testimonial close × sage  accounting customer testimonial close × sage  accounting customer testimonial close × getting around sage  accounting close × sage accounting payroll and payments close × what is sage c close × sage  sage  accounting customer ratings and reviews  out of  stars great product easy to use suits the small to medium business that requires ondemand information —jeffrey b  out of  stars a powerhouse for small and midsize businesses add to that the great price and awesome customer and technical service and you definitely get a bang for your money —karen r  out of  stars sage  rules tax reports are easy to produce with most of the info already input —marsha k  out of  stars i have a snapshot of the business whenever i need it but the real benefit is that it’s user friendly quick and easy to use —clay b  out of  stars sage  works great for construction companies —roxann s  out of  stars it certainly increased efficiency the fact that the three of us in the department could use it simultaneously on different tasks and all be on the same page financially was invaluable —ben c  out of  stars the daytoday work flow is easy to follow and the monthend work like bank reconciliations and closing a month is simple —chris s  out of  stars i have been