sage products include enterprise resource planning erp software payment solutions and cloudbased software as a service saas products for its clients who are based worldwide procurement process it and technology sourcing is managed by the companys procurement department  it structure the it department is manged via a global structure with a functional alignment and regional and location management levels  and previously it priorities • in  sage is continuing its virtualization efforts as well as putting an emphasis on… more it structure the it department is manged via a global structure with a functional alignment and regional and location management levels  and previously it priorities • in  sage is continuing its virtualization efforts as well as putting an emphasis on its storage area network san and its technical architecture it structure • sage groups is department handles operations for information security enterprise development and it operations  • the companys chief technology officer oversees the companys research and development operations which is primarily applicationsfocused  • sages pay subsidiary also has an internal it division of its own with an it security team • sages north american unit as well as sage payment solutions which are subsidiaries of sage group are on rainking as separate profiles please note that the profiles for sage hospitality resources llc and sage products are separate companies and are not part of sage group it bytes • given the nature of sages business as an enterprise resource planning erp software company it uses its own application for that purpose • sage uses hp blade servers in its data centers which are virtualized using vmware solutions • company networks are constructed with cisco hardware • the company allows employees to use blackberry apple and android mobile devices sector industry services business services technology computer software employees  revenue b fye  breaking news on investment signals date type inside 